      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this car is ready to go! I've taken great care of it, and I'd love to see it go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 high-pressure 3.2L inline-six. This unit delivers linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline, supported by a recently serviced double VANOS system and verified valve clearances. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission and the factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. Chassis integrity is excellent; the rear subframe mounting points have been inspected and reinforced, a critical preventative measure for this platform. The suspension utilizes a refreshed MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup with Bilstein B6 dampers for improved rebound control. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the mechanical vitals\u2014including cooling system components and rod bearings\u2014are within optimal operating parameters. A purist-spec driver\u2019s car optimized for technical performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 7
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
