    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with comfort. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch consistent with regular road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and strictly smoke-free; the premium upholstery shows only light bolstering wear, and every electronic feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the infotainment system\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is solid, having undergone a recent multi-point inspection and synthetic oil change. It shifts smoothly through all gears and provides a quiet, composed ride. This is a reliable, attractive car that is ready for its next owner without any immediate maintenance needs.",
      "price": 32500.0,
